dct_title_s: Map of the N.Y.L.E & W.D. & Imp. Co's Yard at Weehawken, N.J.
dct_description_sm: Map data from survey made by the Engineering Department, State Board of Assessors, Oct. 1914.
All bearings referred to True North. Survey notes in Book HL 1-1913, pages 42 to 47, and Book HL 2-1913, pages 16 to 24.
Contains sketch showing location of pierhead and bulkhead lines in front of N.Y.L.E. & W.R.R. Yard at Weehawken, N.J. at scale 1:5000.
